WEBVTT

01:51.860 --> 01:57.460
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.560 --> 02:01.930
[Episode 3]

02:25.710 --> 02:26.710
Your Excellency.

02:27.030 --> 02:28.000
You're back.

02:28.190 --> 02:28.910
Fan Yun?

02:33.240 --> 02:34.240
Why are you here?

02:36.240 --> 02:37.240
I...

02:38.350 --> 02:41.350
I came to apologize to you,
Your Excellency.

02:44.710 --> 02:45.910
Hearing you say the word

02:45.910 --> 02:47.079
makes me unhappy.

02:49.440 --> 02:50.390
What word?

02:52.020 --> 02:53.670
Do you mean the word

02:53.690 --> 02:54.490
"apologize"?

02:55.900 --> 02:57.610
We agreed you'd call me by my name.

02:57.610 --> 02:59.070
Did you forget so quickly?

03:00.790 --> 03:01.510
Yes,

03:02.120 --> 03:02.930
Qi Zheng.

03:04.500 --> 03:07.020
Since you're so uninterested in apologies,

03:07.050 --> 03:08.510
I won't apologize then.

03:08.540 --> 03:09.270
I'm leaving.

03:11.860 --> 03:13.700
It's a rare opportunity.

03:14.060 --> 03:15.780
Tell me your troubles

03:15.780 --> 03:17.340
to make me happy.

03:17.340 --> 03:18.130
You...

03:20.250 --> 03:21.020
Never mind.

03:21.970 --> 03:23.340
I wanted to say

03:23.340 --> 03:25.340
that the memo
sent by the Internal Affairs Department

03:25.340 --> 03:27.020
was buried under my books,

03:27.020 --> 03:29.250
so I delayed the reply.

03:29.250 --> 03:30.570
I was wondering

03:30.570 --> 03:31.650
what I could do to make up for—

03:31.650 --> 03:33.180
Just for such a small thing?

03:34.850 --> 03:35.500
That's it?

03:35.530 --> 03:36.220
That's it.

03:40.850 --> 03:42.300
Could it be that you

03:42.300 --> 03:44.540
want me to make a huge mistake,

03:44.810 --> 03:45.920
so you can condemn me

03:45.920 --> 03:47.990
to eternal ruin?

03:48.720 --> 03:50.210
I have already replied

03:50.650 --> 03:52.510
to the banquet menu issue for you.

03:52.690 --> 03:54.020
You just need to manage it

03:54.020 --> 03:55.350
and show your goodwill.

03:55.900 --> 03:58.000
I believe they won't blame you.

03:58.570 --> 03:59.900
Don't worry.

03:59.900 --> 04:00.900
Really?

04:02.060 --> 04:03.220
Thank you, Your Excellency.

04:03.220 --> 04:04.340
You're so kind.

04:05.690 --> 04:06.890
I wasn't helping you.

04:07.310 --> 04:08.770
I was just helping myself.

04:17.070 --> 04:18.310
You...

04:18.880 --> 04:20.240
I...

04:22.510 --> 04:24.570
Are you going back to the room with me?

04:28.940 --> 04:29.940
I know. I know.

04:30.740 --> 04:32.740
But I'm really tired today.

04:33.250 --> 04:34.250
Take a rain check.

04:34.540 --> 04:36.250
I'll definitely rekindle our romance
another day.

04:36.250 --> 04:36.940
Alright?

04:37.380 --> 04:39.380
What are you fantasizing about?

04:39.400 --> 04:40.130
I...

04:40.159 --> 04:41.659
I just wanted to ask

04:41.860 --> 04:42.890
what gifts you want

04:42.890 --> 04:44.159
for your birthday,

04:44.380 --> 04:45.900
so I can make up for it.

04:50.500 --> 04:52.030
I appreciate your thought,

04:52.500 --> 04:53.730
but I just

04:54.300 --> 04:56.300
don't like celebrating birthdays.

04:56.420 --> 04:57.810
It's just that because of my position,

04:57.810 --> 04:59.010
it's hard to decline.

04:59.890 --> 05:01.420
As for gifts,

05:01.420 --> 05:02.750
others can't skip them,

05:03.330 --> 05:04.620
but Fan Yun,

05:05.180 --> 05:06.130
you can.

05:06.990 --> 05:09.020
Don't like celebrating birthdays?

05:09.570 --> 05:11.180
How strange.

05:12.420 --> 05:14.130
How can that be?

05:14.130 --> 05:15.740
No matter what,

05:15.740 --> 05:17.370
I am your wife.

05:18.100 --> 05:19.180
Besides,

05:19.180 --> 05:20.660
when I make a mistake,

05:20.660 --> 05:22.010
if you don't let me make up for it,

05:22.010 --> 05:23.130
I'll feel bad.

05:23.300 --> 05:24.000
Tell me.

05:24.020 --> 05:25.010
What do you want?

05:25.220 --> 05:27.830
Haven't you always denied being my wife?

05:29.170 --> 05:30.140
Why?

05:30.300 --> 05:32.760
After we spent
these past few days together,

05:33.210 --> 05:34.940
have you fallen in love with me?

05:37.150 --> 05:38.220
In your dreams.

05:38.840 --> 05:40.100
I'm going back to rest.

05:45.010 --> 05:46.060
Why are you spacing out?

05:46.060 --> 05:47.180
Escort her back.

05:51.940 --> 05:53.010
Don't follow me.

05:53.010 --> 05:54.300
I can go back by myself.

05:55.820 --> 05:58.320
[Juyun Pavilion]

06:06.740 --> 06:07.970
Have the identities of the two people

06:07.970 --> 06:09.250
from the past 2 days been verified?

06:09.250 --> 06:11.760
All the pawnshops have received the news.

06:12.180 --> 06:13.010
But

06:13.010 --> 06:14.340
we've asked everywhere

06:14.340 --> 06:16.940
and haven't found
any information about them.

06:21.320 --> 06:23.440
Go and tell all the silk shops

06:23.570 --> 06:24.980
to keep an eye out for anyone

06:24.980 --> 06:27.330
who has bought
similar silk threads recently.

06:27.330 --> 06:28.810
They might want to imitate

06:28.810 --> 06:30.250
the fabrics of Juyun Pavilion,

06:30.250 --> 06:32.860
pass off inferior goods as high quality,
and make money from it.

06:32.860 --> 06:34.620
What about Huan'e House?

06:34.620 --> 06:35.740
Do we still take it?

06:39.010 --> 06:42.770
The only thing worth mentioning about
Huan'e House is their tribute wine.

06:42.770 --> 06:44.230
As for the other things...

06:47.659 --> 06:49.120
I don't think much of them.

06:50.300 --> 06:52.060
The first-grade tribute wine
from Huan'e House

06:52.060 --> 06:54.540
is full-bodied with a deep red hue.

06:54.540 --> 06:55.620
It's spicy but not hot.

06:55.620 --> 06:57.300
It's the best of the best.

06:57.810 --> 06:59.740
If we could see it with our own eyes,

06:59.840 --> 07:00.960
maybe,

07:00.980 --> 07:03.110
we could imitate 70 to 80 percent of it.

07:20.980 --> 07:22.770
Tomorrow is His Excellency's birthday.

07:22.770 --> 07:24.190
Could it be that you

07:24.460 --> 07:27.810
want to give these wines to him?

07:28.560 --> 07:29.760
These wines

07:29.780 --> 07:32.180
have all been presented in previous years.

07:32.570 --> 07:33.659
It's just that this year,

07:33.659 --> 07:36.620
no particularly good wine
has been produced yet.

07:36.620 --> 07:38.540
Why not let me choose this year?

07:41.659 --> 07:43.260
My good grandson.

07:55.620 --> 07:56.810
This is wheat liquor.

07:56.810 --> 07:58.740
It was bought from the distillery
under Juyun Pavilion.

07:58.740 --> 08:00.890
It's clean and sweet.

08:00.890 --> 08:03.350
It's a top-quality product
in recent years.

08:10.860 --> 08:12.100
Indeed, good liquor.

08:13.130 --> 08:14.010
Look. Look.

08:14.010 --> 08:15.660
We've taken advantage
of His Excellency's luck

08:15.660 --> 08:16.890
to have a taste.

08:18.100 --> 08:19.180
After entering Ling'an,

08:19.180 --> 08:20.860
I have never entered
the Governor Residence.

08:20.860 --> 08:22.520
Why not take this opportunity

08:22.620 --> 08:25.080
to let me follow you
and broaden my horizons?

08:27.250 --> 08:28.100
-You.
-You.

08:29.060 --> 08:32.260
-Are a really good grandson.
-Are a really good grandson.

08:38.289 --> 08:39.480
-Come on.
-Come on.

08:45.380 --> 08:46.610
It's said that

08:46.610 --> 08:48.670
handsome men gather in Ling'an City.

08:49.060 --> 08:50.810
Take the Governor as an example.

08:50.070 --> 08:52.410
[Wei Ying,
the noble daughter of the Wei family]

08:50.810 --> 08:53.330
He is a top handsome man in the main hall,

08:53.330 --> 08:55.260
ranking second on the Guanyu List.

08:56.970 --> 08:59.210
But doesn't he have a wife?

09:09.090 --> 09:09.940
Wei Rong,

09:09.940 --> 09:11.060
stop playing!

09:13.090 --> 09:15.540
Fair faces end in bare bones.
Fine men soon fade with time.

09:15.540 --> 09:17.900
The Governor Residence
is not a good place.

09:17.900 --> 09:19.810
It's full of intrigue
in such a small space.

09:19.810 --> 09:21.540
Such a simple person like you

09:21.540 --> 09:23.600
can easily lose yourself if you go in.

09:24.020 --> 09:25.260
What do you know?

09:25.300 --> 09:27.140
Marrying the second-ranked man
on the Guanyu List

09:27.140 --> 09:28.570
comes at a cost.

09:28.570 --> 09:29.570
This time,

09:29.570 --> 09:31.730
I want to live a different life!

09:32.510 --> 09:34.640
[Wei Rong,
the noble son of the Wei family]

10:14.260 --> 10:15.260
Lord Yan Jiang.

10:16.170 --> 10:17.100
Don't run away.

10:17.380 --> 10:18.800
You just came from over there.

10:18.800 --> 10:20.670
Don't go back again.

10:22.140 --> 10:23.020
My Lady.

10:23.020 --> 10:24.090
Why is it you?

10:24.090 --> 10:24.810
What a coincidence.

10:24.810 --> 10:26.020
It's not a coincidence at all.

10:26.020 --> 10:28.020
I've been waiting for you right here.

10:28.020 --> 10:28.900
Waiting for me?

10:29.780 --> 10:32.110
How did you know I would pass by here?

10:32.250 --> 10:33.450
Because...

10:34.280 --> 10:35.750
because ordinary people

10:36.220 --> 10:37.930
wouldn't be able to walk here.

10:37.950 --> 10:39.310
So I just waited here.

10:39.340 --> 10:40.910
Only you would appear here.

10:41.540 --> 10:42.730
I am speechless.

10:43.870 --> 10:44.750
Lord Yan,

10:44.810 --> 10:46.710
I have something to ask you.

10:47.130 --> 10:48.720
It seems His Excellency

10:49.180 --> 10:50.780
really doesn't want to celebrate
his birthday.

10:50.780 --> 10:52.110
Why is that?

10:55.450 --> 10:56.450
It is...

10:56.450 --> 10:57.970
a long story.

10:57.970 --> 10:59.900
It's hard to explain in a few words.

11:01.610 --> 11:02.610
Let's get to work.

11:42.330 --> 11:43.900
What time is it now?

11:43.900 --> 11:45.830
Why hasn't breakfast been served?

11:46.210 --> 11:47.380
Please wait a moment, Your Excellency.

11:47.380 --> 11:49.040
Breakfast will be ready soon.

11:54.610 --> 11:55.300
Forget it.

11:56.140 --> 11:57.670
I'm not in a good mood today.

11:58.330 --> 11:59.140
Just skip it.

12:01.090 --> 12:02.260
How can that be?

12:02.260 --> 12:03.300
Your Excellency.

12:03.300 --> 12:04.300
Your Excellency.

12:04.730 --> 12:06.620
How can you not have breakfast?

12:06.940 --> 12:07.810
Fan Yun?

12:08.610 --> 12:09.570
Why are you here?

12:12.610 --> 12:13.660
I am, of course,

12:14.140 --> 12:16.260
here to bring you breakfast.

12:23.370 --> 12:24.210
You cooked...

12:24.260 --> 12:25.340
cooked all morning

12:25.360 --> 12:26.560
and only made one egg?

12:28.840 --> 12:29.650
Your Excellency.

12:29.650 --> 12:31.380
Don't underestimate this egg.

12:31.490 --> 12:33.330
It has a great purpose.

12:35.300 --> 12:36.330
Come on, sit nicely.

12:36.330 --> 12:38.190
-What are you doing?
-Sit nicely.

12:48.090 --> 12:50.380
Roll away the bad luck.

12:52.060 --> 12:54.860
Roll in the good luck.

12:56.940 --> 12:59.940
Roll away the villains.

13:02.380 --> 13:05.690
Roll in the benefactors.

13:10.090 --> 13:13.020
Roll away the diseases.

13:14.140 --> 13:17.610
Roll in good health.

13:19.060 --> 13:19.860
Roll...

13:20.180 --> 13:20.900
No way.

13:23.090 --> 13:24.060
This won't do.

13:25.840 --> 13:26.840
This won't do?

13:28.420 --> 13:29.490
-I mean…
-Alright.

13:30.210 --> 13:31.330
What is this for?

13:32.780 --> 13:34.210
Bad luck rolls away,

13:34.210 --> 13:35.940
and a year of good times begins.

13:36.470 --> 13:37.860
Once I peel this egg,

13:38.160 --> 13:39.160
you can eat it.

13:40.570 --> 13:42.180
I have to eat it?

13:42.180 --> 13:44.250
It's like this now. Can it still be eaten?

13:44.250 --> 13:45.560
Why can't it be eaten?

13:46.610 --> 13:47.810
Only by eating it

13:47.810 --> 13:51.140
will all your bad luck
for the year vanish.

13:52.020 --> 13:53.600
Where did this custom come from?

13:53.600 --> 13:54.790
I've never heard of it.

13:54.790 --> 13:55.950
I'm not eating it.

13:56.940 --> 13:59.180
But when I was sick as a child,

13:59.540 --> 14:00.450
my mother used

14:00.450 --> 14:02.050
to roll an egg on me like this.

14:02.960 --> 14:04.320
Not long ago,

14:04.380 --> 14:05.510
for his birthday,

14:05.530 --> 14:07.260
my father boiled an egg for himself

14:07.260 --> 14:08.860
and burned down the kitchen.

14:09.450 --> 14:11.980
Since then, I've never
rolled eggs on anyone.

14:14.610 --> 14:15.610
You should eat it.

14:15.610 --> 14:16.620
It really works.

14:20.470 --> 14:22.400
Then it's enough if I eat it, right?

14:30.710 --> 14:31.710
I've finished it.

14:32.090 --> 14:32.690
And...

14:34.120 --> 14:35.430
Where are you going?

14:35.450 --> 14:36.170
Well...

14:36.570 --> 14:37.260
I...

14:37.260 --> 14:39.540
Y-You haven't had the most important meal

14:39.540 --> 14:40.570
of the morning today.

14:40.570 --> 14:41.570
There's more?

14:41.600 --> 14:42.520
Of course.

14:49.660 --> 14:51.060
Listen, Your Excellency,

14:51.060 --> 14:51.940
you have to finish every last bite

14:51.940 --> 14:54.140
of this bowl of noodles.

14:54.140 --> 14:54.810
It took me

14:54.810 --> 14:56.380
a lot of effort to make it.

14:57.450 --> 14:59.380
You can't leave a single bite.

15:01.420 --> 15:03.060
Try it first, come on.

15:17.280 --> 15:18.280
Qi Zheng.

15:23.240 --> 15:24.330
Congratulations.

15:24.360 --> 15:25.630
You're a year older.

15:29.090 --> 15:30.020
Second Brother,

15:30.020 --> 15:31.850
why do you always cook pig trotter noodles

15:31.850 --> 15:33.850
for my birthday every year?

15:35.110 --> 15:36.440
Mother said

15:36.460 --> 15:38.610
pig trotter soup is the most nourishing.

15:38.610 --> 15:39.970
You should eat more

15:39.970 --> 15:41.090
to grow up fast

15:41.090 --> 15:42.660
and stronger,

15:42.660 --> 15:44.690
so no one will dare to bully you.

15:48.300 --> 15:48.970
Slow down.

15:48.970 --> 15:50.300
Be careful not to choke.

15:51.330 --> 15:52.420
Eat slowly.

15:57.330 --> 15:59.940
I want to be as strong as you,

15:59.940 --> 16:01.210
so I won't be bullied,

16:01.210 --> 16:02.900
and I can bully others.

16:03.880 --> 16:05.550
We won't let others bully us,

16:05.850 --> 16:07.710
but we can't bully others either.

16:08.010 --> 16:10.010
Look at him, look.

16:10.030 --> 16:11.150
So disgusting.

16:17.120 --> 16:18.000
Does it hurt?

16:18.490 --> 16:19.970
Did they bully you again?

16:21.320 --> 16:22.680
It's fine, Second Brother.

16:22.680 --> 16:24.160
It doesn't hurt anymore.

16:35.480 --> 16:36.670
He's coming.

16:36.700 --> 16:38.420
-Let's go.
-Come on.

16:57.970 --> 16:59.500
It doesn't taste like that?

17:02.260 --> 17:03.850
It shouldn't be.

17:04.420 --> 17:06.400
I put so much effort into making it.

17:06.859 --> 17:08.750
How could it be so hard to swallow?

17:09.079 --> 17:09.990
Let me taste it.

17:29.970 --> 17:31.030
Your Excellency,

17:31.070 --> 17:32.000
how does it

17:32.530 --> 17:33.380
taste?

17:37.820 --> 17:40.620
The taste of this bowl of noodles
is very familiar.

17:41.450 --> 17:43.250
I haven't eaten it in a long time.

17:44.380 --> 17:45.620
The last time I ate it

17:46.010 --> 17:47.860
was on my birthday.

17:49.450 --> 17:51.250
My second brother made it for me.

17:55.220 --> 17:57.280
I like this bowl of noodles very much.

17:59.770 --> 18:01.140
That's great.

18:01.140 --> 18:02.730
The bad luck is gone,

18:02.730 --> 18:04.390
and the noodles are finished.

18:05.420 --> 18:06.730
How did you know

18:07.490 --> 18:09.020
about this bowl of noodles?

18:10.180 --> 18:11.250
Well...

18:13.340 --> 18:15.660
I asked Lord Yan Jiang about it.

18:16.730 --> 18:17.730
Your Excellency,

18:18.210 --> 18:19.860
anyway,

18:19.860 --> 18:21.450
I think

18:21.450 --> 18:22.920
time is fair.

18:23.250 --> 18:25.110
The good and the bad will all pass.

18:25.600 --> 18:26.640
So,

18:26.660 --> 18:28.460
we should cherish the present,

18:28.530 --> 18:29.590
live in the moment,

18:30.010 --> 18:31.220
and live out

18:31.690 --> 18:33.340
our true selves.

18:38.620 --> 18:39.770
You know what?

18:41.660 --> 18:43.620
Ever since my second brother left,

18:44.990 --> 18:46.540
I've felt like

18:46.690 --> 18:48.820
there's a huge gaping hole in my heart.

18:55.250 --> 18:56.310
Somehow,

18:57.610 --> 18:59.890
it seems to be filled up again today.

19:02.010 --> 19:03.620
Thank you, Fan Yun.

19:06.400 --> 19:07.640
But

19:07.690 --> 19:09.150
you still haven't told me.

19:11.460 --> 19:13.060
Whose side are you really on?

19:14.480 --> 19:15.320
I...

19:19.450 --> 19:21.100
You want to ask

19:21.820 --> 19:24.620
about the 3 dresses with different colors,
right?

19:24.970 --> 19:26.830
The Three Elders sent the dresses

19:27.340 --> 19:28.860
presumably with good intentions.

19:28.860 --> 19:30.380
So I took one color from each

19:30.380 --> 19:31.640
to make a single dress.

19:32.580 --> 19:33.640
This should

19:33.860 --> 19:35.460
stand as my position, right?

19:43.730 --> 19:44.810
Then I understand.

19:45.940 --> 19:47.210
From now on,

19:49.340 --> 19:50.900
you are my person.

20:15.100 --> 20:16.730
Don't pull it apart with too much force

20:16.730 --> 20:17.940
or make it too big.

20:17.940 --> 20:20.470
-Each fits perfectly in one mouthful.
-Okay.

20:20.820 --> 20:21.690
My Lady.

20:22.920 --> 20:23.840
Suyin.

20:25.690 --> 20:26.820
Lord Zheng Yuan is here.

20:26.820 --> 20:28.620
Do you want to avoid him for now?

20:29.010 --> 20:30.290
Lord Zheng?

20:31.500 --> 20:33.390
Today is His Excellency's birthday.

20:33.390 --> 20:34.550
No need to hide.

20:35.280 --> 20:36.630
He is...

20:37.010 --> 20:38.280
probably here

20:38.800 --> 20:40.030
looking for me.

20:48.050 --> 20:48.900
My Lady.

20:49.560 --> 20:50.640
My Lady.

20:51.470 --> 20:52.910
Greetings, Lord Zheng.

20:52.960 --> 20:55.280
I was heading to the banquet.

20:55.300 --> 20:57.500
I just happened to pass by

20:57.620 --> 20:59.100
and wanted to see

20:59.100 --> 21:00.960
how the preparations were going.

21:01.140 --> 21:03.860
Since you are working hard here,

21:05.340 --> 21:08.860
I came over to greet you.

21:08.860 --> 21:10.050
Thank you, Lord Zheng.

21:10.050 --> 21:12.490
It's all my duty.

21:13.450 --> 21:15.700
Then you should also know

21:15.820 --> 21:17.280
that there are some things

21:17.820 --> 21:20.580
you shouldn't do, right?

21:26.010 --> 21:28.010
As far as I know,

21:28.770 --> 21:30.400
lately, you have had

21:30.830 --> 21:32.620
your own opinions

21:32.690 --> 21:34.590
on the residence's affairs,

21:35.620 --> 21:37.210
or even, quite a few

21:37.450 --> 21:38.960
complaints.

21:41.160 --> 21:42.560
May I ask, Lord Zheng,

21:43.010 --> 21:44.710
what exactly are you referring to?

21:44.710 --> 21:45.960
No matter what,

21:47.380 --> 21:50.110
no matter how noble your status is,

21:50.580 --> 21:52.070
you are still a woman.

21:52.470 --> 21:53.710
Women

21:53.730 --> 21:54.600
should

21:55.180 --> 21:56.970
mind their words and actions,

21:58.210 --> 22:01.050
and do what they are supposed to do.

22:01.940 --> 22:03.530
Keep to yourself,

22:03.940 --> 22:04.880
and especially,

22:05.250 --> 22:09.900
don't make wild comments
about the affairs of the residence.

22:10.140 --> 22:11.060
Otherwise,

22:11.820 --> 22:14.660
since what's said without intent
might be taken to heart by listeners,

22:14.660 --> 22:15.650
I'm afraid

22:16.040 --> 22:18.330
it will bring unnecessary trouble.

22:20.190 --> 22:20.930
But...

22:22.730 --> 22:23.580
But...

22:24.420 --> 22:25.970
But...

22:26.460 --> 22:27.450
listen.

22:29.290 --> 22:32.460
Even the cicadas on this tree
have the right to make a sound,

22:32.460 --> 22:34.420
so why can't I?

22:38.860 --> 22:40.150
Besides, what I said

22:40.450 --> 22:41.750
is all beneficial

22:42.380 --> 22:43.580
to the residence.

22:43.820 --> 22:45.750
I don't see anything wrong with it.

22:49.520 --> 22:51.150
In that case,

22:51.170 --> 22:52.610
I will take my leave.

22:54.340 --> 22:55.010
Let me see you out.

22:55.010 --> 22:55.970
No need.

23:01.580 --> 23:02.360
My Lady.

23:03.100 --> 23:04.830
I will see Lord Zheng Yuan out for you.

23:04.830 --> 23:05.510
Go ahead.

23:18.260 --> 23:19.680
The great affairs of the Nine Cities

23:19.680 --> 23:22.130
are not for women to meddle.

23:23.340 --> 23:25.000
A female ruling in man's stead

23:25.800 --> 23:27.670
bodes chaos and ruin.

23:29.250 --> 23:30.940
Beauty is a curse

23:32.340 --> 23:34.100
and must not remain.

23:36.380 --> 23:37.910
Take care, Lord Zheng Yuan.

23:57.940 --> 23:59.010
Stop right there.

24:00.320 --> 24:01.490
Release your grip.

24:02.110 --> 24:03.800
Head up. Chest out.

24:04.660 --> 24:06.860
A girl should act like a girl.

24:07.320 --> 24:08.150
Continue.

24:17.090 --> 24:18.290
Alright, alright.

24:18.310 --> 24:19.980
Just walk normally.

24:20.050 --> 24:20.970
Okay?

24:23.470 --> 24:26.250
Is His Excellency really
the second most handsome in the world?

24:26.250 --> 24:27.510
Well...

24:28.010 --> 24:29.540
Second is nothing special.

24:30.190 --> 24:32.580
The residence is full of old men
at the age of the Three Elders.

24:32.580 --> 24:35.040
Qi Zheng is the only man
of marriageable age,

24:35.180 --> 24:37.140
yet he can't even rank first.

24:37.730 --> 24:39.060
You, Wei Rong!

24:39.780 --> 24:41.060
When did you get here?

24:42.210 --> 24:43.870
I've been here the whole time.

24:44.050 --> 24:45.530
Is what he said true?

24:48.290 --> 24:50.010
The lords in Ling'an

24:50.010 --> 24:52.690
are indeed a bit on the older side.

24:52.720 --> 24:54.650
-But—
-He can't even be number one?

24:55.180 --> 24:57.530
Yet you said His Excellency
is the second most handsome in the world.

24:57.530 --> 24:59.180
Weren't you two lying to me?

24:59.180 --> 24:59.730
I'm not going.

24:59.730 --> 25:01.150
I want to go home, back to Gao City.

25:01.150 --> 25:02.280
No, no.

25:03.340 --> 25:05.340
Even if you are as free as the wind,

25:05.340 --> 25:07.250
you can't escape the shackles of the world

25:07.250 --> 25:09.530
or the bonds of family.

25:09.530 --> 25:10.770
Once you enter the residence,

25:10.770 --> 25:12.250
you can't come and go as you please.

25:12.250 --> 25:13.380
Shut up.

25:17.900 --> 25:19.380
My good sister,

25:19.380 --> 25:20.190
just treat it

25:20.900 --> 25:22.210
as a visit to the Qi Residence,

25:22.210 --> 25:22.940
right?

25:22.940 --> 25:24.270
Just take a walk around.

25:24.660 --> 25:27.260
His Excellency won't force you
into anything.

25:27.420 --> 25:29.490
How can you guarantee for him?

25:29.490 --> 25:31.050
Will a beautiful,

25:31.050 --> 25:32.410
exquisite woman like me

25:32.410 --> 25:34.210
be allowed to come and go freely?

25:37.250 --> 25:39.980
Why do I feel like
you're quite proud of yourself?

25:40.440 --> 25:41.370
Never mind.

25:41.420 --> 25:42.220
I understand.

25:42.730 --> 25:43.860
Shisan, you're tired

25:43.860 --> 25:46.050
of being a bird flying freely in the sky

25:46.050 --> 25:48.380
and want to be a canary
in a deep courtyard.

25:54.820 --> 25:56.050
A song of "Caged Bird"

25:56.050 --> 25:57.180
to bid you farewell.

26:02.800 --> 26:04.530
Stop playing. I'm telling you.

26:04.820 --> 26:05.780
Wei Rong.

26:06.140 --> 26:07.300
If you keep playing...

26:07.300 --> 26:09.160
I'll kill you if you keep playing!

26:09.960 --> 26:11.870
You took my sword again!

26:13.210 --> 26:14.240
Stop running!

26:14.300 --> 26:15.540
I'm telling you,

26:15.690 --> 26:16.940
if I catch you, I'll kill you!

26:16.940 --> 26:18.180
Catch me if you have the guts!

26:18.180 --> 26:18.900
Come here!

26:18.900 --> 26:20.000
Both of you, stop!

26:47.110 --> 26:49.310
Looks like there's a good show to watch.

26:53.690 --> 26:54.290
Young Master Shi,

26:54.290 --> 26:55.380
the Master wants you to go over quickly.

26:55.380 --> 26:57.210
His Excellency is arriving soon.

26:57.210 --> 26:58.740
I won't offer liquor today.

26:59.020 --> 26:59.990
How can that be?

27:00.410 --> 27:02.350
We came today to offer liquor.

27:02.730 --> 27:03.530
If we don't offer it,

27:03.530 --> 27:05.390
how do we explain it to the Master?

27:15.290 --> 27:16.290
Get out of the way!

27:18.770 --> 27:19.620
Come here!

27:28.500 --> 27:29.740
Help!

27:33.030 --> 27:33.700
Who are you?

27:33.720 --> 27:35.210
How dare you commit a crime
with a sword here?

27:35.210 --> 27:36.670
Capture her immediately!

27:41.260 --> 27:42.450
A song of "Po Zhen Zi"

27:42.450 --> 27:43.910
to embolden you warriors.

28:12.880 --> 28:13.850
Shisan,

28:13.940 --> 28:14.820
listen to my explanation.

28:14.820 --> 28:15.730
What explanation?

28:15.730 --> 28:19.190
I wouldn't deserve the surname Wei
if I don't beat you up today!

28:30.640 --> 28:33.000
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

28:33.030 --> 28:34.480
♪ Over the whole town ♪

28:34.510 --> 28:37.160
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

28:37.330 --> 28:40.830
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

28:45.900 --> 28:47.050
This is a restricted area
of the Qi Residence.

28:47.050 --> 28:48.340
You used weapons without permission.

28:48.340 --> 28:49.970
Return with me to receive your punishment.

28:49.970 --> 28:51.380
Good looking.

28:55.100 --> 28:56.560
Are you going to arrest me?

28:57.890 --> 28:59.150
How will you arrest me?

28:59.160 --> 29:00.440
Will you tie my hands?

29:01.090 --> 29:02.680
Do you like tying hands

29:02.770 --> 29:03.940
or feet?

29:05.010 --> 29:05.860
Tie me up.

29:05.860 --> 29:07.250
Hurry up and tie me up.

29:08.380 --> 29:09.010
Catch me.

29:09.040 --> 29:10.770
Please behave yourself, Miss.

29:10.820 --> 29:13.080
Misunderstanding! Misunderstanding!

29:15.210 --> 29:17.880
Gao Ran, this is my younger sister.

29:17.970 --> 29:19.570
She's a little mischievous.

29:20.940 --> 29:21.900
Lord Wei,

29:21.900 --> 29:23.900
your sister used a weapon
in the restricted area

29:23.900 --> 29:25.250
and injured my people.

29:25.250 --> 29:26.690
No matter who she is,

29:26.690 --> 29:27.860
I must bring her back to the residence

29:27.860 --> 29:29.770
to confess her crimes
and accept punishment.

29:29.770 --> 29:30.510
Guard Gao.

29:31.050 --> 29:32.250
My sister came today

29:32.250 --> 29:33.180
for an audience.

29:33.310 --> 29:34.310
So,

29:34.490 --> 29:35.940
please be lenient, Guard Gao.

29:35.940 --> 29:36.670
An audience?

29:36.890 --> 29:37.690
It's fine if I don't see him.

29:37.690 --> 29:38.730
Say less.

29:42.480 --> 29:43.390
Lord Wei,

29:43.530 --> 29:44.780
I'll leave you two to it.

29:44.780 --> 29:46.180
I won't keep you company.

29:49.900 --> 29:51.100
Thank you, Guard Gao.

29:56.680 --> 29:57.530
Brother,

29:57.580 --> 29:58.380
who is he?

29:58.380 --> 29:59.490
Why do you care who he is?

29:59.490 --> 30:00.690
You caused such a big mess today.

30:00.690 --> 30:01.870
I haven't settled the score with you yet.

30:01.870 --> 30:03.470
The birthday banquet is about to begin.

30:03.470 --> 30:04.490
Hurry up and come with me.

30:04.490 --> 30:05.290
I'm not going.

30:05.320 --> 30:06.040
What?

30:06.730 --> 30:07.970
I've found the one.

30:08.860 --> 30:09.950
Found who?

30:11.770 --> 30:13.030
The man I want to marry.

30:17.850 --> 30:20.050
Don't tell me you've fallen for Gao Ran.

30:20.490 --> 30:21.770
Gao Ran.

30:22.770 --> 30:24.230
Even his name sounds nice.

30:25.400 --> 30:27.050
I don't care who you fancy.

30:27.580 --> 30:29.660
You still have to attend
His Excellency's birthday banquet.

30:29.660 --> 30:31.060
Hurry up and come with me.

30:32.250 --> 30:33.450
Let me tell you,

30:33.450 --> 30:34.940
you only have 2 choices today.

30:34.940 --> 30:36.340
First one, let me go.

30:36.340 --> 30:38.180
Second, I'll die right in front of you.

30:38.180 --> 30:39.250
I'm so beautiful

30:39.250 --> 30:40.180
and good at martial arts.

30:40.180 --> 30:41.010
What if His Excellency sees me

30:41.010 --> 30:42.270
and won't let me leave?

30:42.480 --> 30:43.380
Let's talk this out.

30:43.380 --> 30:43.970
Put the sword down.

30:43.970 --> 30:44.730
I won't.

30:46.290 --> 30:47.570
My lovely sister,

30:47.600 --> 30:49.150
it's good to be confident.

30:49.210 --> 30:50.340
But what if...

30:50.440 --> 30:52.820
what if His Excellency
doesn't even like you?

30:52.820 --> 30:53.620
Right?

30:57.900 --> 30:58.860
Fine, fine.

30:58.900 --> 31:00.550
-Go. Go.
-Take it.

31:02.690 --> 31:03.560
Let me tell you,

31:03.690 --> 31:05.420
don't come back once you leave!

31:09.290 --> 31:10.290
Wei Rong!

31:12.420 --> 31:13.290
Wei Rong!

31:15.420 --> 31:16.220
These two...

31:16.790 --> 31:17.950
It's truly...

31:17.980 --> 31:20.380
It's truly a misfortune
for our Wei family!

31:50.770 --> 31:53.620
His Excellency has arrived!

32:04.990 --> 32:08.450
-Greetings, Your Excellency.
-Greetings, Your Excellency.

32:13.770 --> 32:14.960
You may rise.

32:15.450 --> 32:18.780
-Thank you, Your Excellency.
-Thank you, Your Excellency.

32:37.000 --> 32:37.910
Come on.

32:52.590 --> 32:53.310
Careful.

33:02.660 --> 33:04.260
Thank you, Your Excellency.

33:05.320 --> 33:07.050
Don't let anything befall you.

33:07.470 --> 33:08.320
Otherwise, I

33:08.640 --> 33:10.250
won't know what to do.

33:19.630 --> 33:20.520
Careful.

33:54.100 --> 33:55.050
My Beloved,

33:55.050 --> 33:56.140
here,

33:56.140 --> 33:57.210
try this.

33:57.900 --> 33:59.000
I know we are acting,

33:59.000 --> 34:00.380
but act a little more naturally.

34:00.380 --> 34:02.090
You're acting really weird.

34:02.410 --> 34:04.010
The more exaggerated we are,

34:04.230 --> 34:05.730
the more noticeable we become.

34:05.730 --> 34:06.770
Hurry and try it.

34:08.570 --> 34:09.340
Okay.

34:13.650 --> 34:14.489
Is it good?

34:15.179 --> 34:16.239
Yes.

34:16.510 --> 34:17.560
Then eat more.

34:26.380 --> 34:27.480
Your Excellency.

34:28.010 --> 34:29.409
Look, who is the young man

34:29.699 --> 34:31.739
sitting behind Lord Zheng?

34:33.940 --> 34:37.010
Why does he look so familiar?

34:39.010 --> 34:40.219
I'm right in front of you,

34:40.219 --> 34:42.219
yet you are discussing another man.

34:42.420 --> 34:43.750
Watch the performance.

34:54.130 --> 34:55.790
You eat too, Your Excellency.

34:57.570 --> 34:58.260
Great!

34:58.700 --> 34:59.550
Well danced!

34:59.900 --> 35:00.740
Great!

35:02.040 --> 35:02.880
Great.

35:17.040 --> 35:18.560
-Have some more.
-You too.

35:18.600 --> 35:20.530
Happy birthday, Your Excellency.

35:20.610 --> 35:21.610
Your Excellency,

35:21.860 --> 35:23.570
may you live long and prosper.

35:23.570 --> 35:25.420
-Happy birthday, Your Excellency.
-Happy birthday, Your Excellency.

35:25.420 --> 35:28.490
-May you live long and prosper.
-May you live long and prosper.

35:28.490 --> 35:29.650
Your Excellency, you've had

35:29.650 --> 35:31.320
a lot of good news lately.

35:31.700 --> 35:34.340
Seeing how affectionate you two are,

35:34.340 --> 35:35.140
I

35:35.380 --> 35:36.940
can rest assured.

35:38.300 --> 35:39.970
I hope you and your wife

35:39.970 --> 35:42.050
will have a child soon

35:42.780 --> 35:45.380
to continue the prosperity
of our Nine Cities.

35:45.970 --> 35:48.300
Thank you for your kind words, Lord Zheng.

35:48.650 --> 35:49.610
We...

35:51.970 --> 35:54.230
will certainly live up to expectations.

35:54.820 --> 35:55.780
That's you.

35:55.780 --> 35:57.450
Don't drag me into this.

36:02.510 --> 36:04.510
Since you took office,

36:04.540 --> 36:06.940
there have been few heirs
in the residence.

36:07.260 --> 36:08.860
But don't worry.

36:08.860 --> 36:11.420
I have discussed it with everyone.

36:11.780 --> 36:14.610
We should select noble women

36:14.610 --> 36:17.110
to fill the inner quarters
and have more children,

36:17.110 --> 36:19.570
to strengthen the bloodline
of the Qi family.

36:19.570 --> 36:19.970
Well...

36:19.970 --> 36:22.340
Today, there's a lady from the Wei family.

36:23.130 --> 36:24.590
She is dignified

36:24.970 --> 36:26.450
and gentle.

36:26.450 --> 36:27.130
I am...

36:27.900 --> 36:29.130
still young.

36:29.130 --> 36:30.700
Filling the inner quarters

36:31.080 --> 36:32.000
can wait.

36:33.300 --> 36:35.680
Anything involving you

36:36.050 --> 36:37.210
is a big deal.

36:37.480 --> 36:40.400
Your heir involves Nine Cities.

36:40.530 --> 36:42.620
It's not just a personal matter.

36:44.170 --> 36:45.830
Among all the world's charms,

36:45.900 --> 36:46.970
I desire but one.

36:47.820 --> 36:48.530
Besides,

36:48.530 --> 36:50.330
I already have my wife by my side.

36:50.610 --> 36:51.670
I'm afraid my heart

36:51.790 --> 36:53.320
has no room for anyone else.

36:53.530 --> 36:55.010
Right, My Beloved?

36:58.420 --> 37:00.570
You haven't even seen her yet.

37:00.570 --> 37:02.820
How do you know there's no room for her?

37:03.740 --> 37:06.300
Please invite Lady Wei in.

37:10.510 --> 37:12.110
This... this is...

37:12.130 --> 37:13.050
A man?

37:25.070 --> 37:27.840
Hurry up and invite Lady Wei in.

37:31.010 --> 37:32.340
On my sister's way here,

37:32.340 --> 37:33.740
the horse pulling the carriage
was frightened.

37:33.740 --> 37:34.860
The carriage overturned,

37:34.860 --> 37:36.860
and she was unfortunately injured.

37:37.340 --> 37:38.540
In my sister's heart,

37:38.740 --> 37:41.170
Your Excellency, you're like the sun
high in the sky.

37:41.170 --> 37:42.610
She felt inadequate

37:42.640 --> 37:43.910
and unworthy of you.

37:43.930 --> 37:45.130
She didn't deserve to see you.

37:45.130 --> 37:46.010
Halfway here,

37:46.010 --> 37:47.090
she left silently.

37:47.090 --> 37:48.380
Did Wei Shisan

37:49.050 --> 37:50.300
go home?

37:50.970 --> 37:53.090
Fate is truly playing tricks on us.

37:56.700 --> 37:57.780
I am deeply sympathetic

37:57.780 --> 37:59.440
to your sister's misfortune.

37:59.740 --> 38:01.800
Seems I have to disappoint you again.

38:02.340 --> 38:04.420
Come on, give Lord Wei a seat!
